## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="0e18b-102"><xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView>控件都将引发<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView.ItemUpdated>事件时<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView.UpdateItem%2A>调用方法，或单击控件中的更新按钮后时，但之后<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView>控件更新该项。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0e18b-102">The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView> control raises the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView.ItemUpdated> event when the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView.UpdateItem%2A> method is called or when an Update button in the control is clicked, but after the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView> control updates the item.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0e18b-103">(的更新按钮控件是一个按钮其`CommandName`属性设置为"更新"。)这使你能够在每次此事件发生时，例如检查更新操作的结果执行的自定义的例程的事件处理方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0e18b-103">(An Update button is a button whose `CommandName` property is set to "Update".) This enables you to provide an event-handling method that performs a custom routine whenever this event occurs, such as checking the results of an update operation.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0e18b-104">A<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewUpdatedEventArgs>对象传递给事件处理方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0e18b-104">A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewUpdatedEventArgs> object is passed to the event-handling method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0e18b-105">此对象使您可以确定更新的项的数目，并以获取可能已经发生的任何异常。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0e18b-105">This object enables you to determine the number of items updated and to get any exceptions that might have occurred.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0e18b-106">若要确定受更新操作的项的数目，使用<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewUpdatedEventArgs.AffectedRows%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0e18b-106">To determine the number of items that were affected by the update operation, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewUpdatedEventArgs.AffectedRows%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0e18b-107">若要确定是否发生任何异常，请使用<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewUpdatedEventArgs.Exception%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0e18b-107">To determine whether any exceptions occurred, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewUpdatedEventArgs.Exception%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0e18b-108">你可以指示是否处理了异常事件处理方法中通过设置<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewUpdatedEventArgs.ExceptionHandled%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0e18b-108">You can indicate whether the exception was handled in the event-handling method by setting the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewUpdatedEventArgs.ExceptionHandled%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0e18b-109">你可以通过访问字段的原始值<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewUpdatedEventArgs.OldValues%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0e18b-109">You can access the original field values by using the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewUpdatedEventArgs.OldValues%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0e18b-110">你可以通过访问更新的字段值<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewUpdatedEventArgs.NewValues%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0e18b-110">You can access updated field values by using the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewUpdatedEventArgs.NewValues%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0e18b-111">默认情况下，<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView>项后更新操作将返回到只读模式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0e18b-111">By default, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView> item returns to read-only mode after an update operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0e18b-112">如果你处理更新操作过程中发生的异常，则可以保留<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView>处于编辑模式，通过设置项<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewUpdatedEventArgs.KeepInEditMode%2A>属性`true`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0e18b-112">If you handle an exception that occurred during the update operation, you can keep the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView> item in edit mode by setting the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewUpdatedEventArgs.KeepInEditMode%2A> property to `true`.</span></span>  
  
